&lt;p&gt; &lt;em&gt;Thấy hiền so sánh trừ tạp niệm   Tam tâm&lt;a href=&quot;#_ftn4&quot; name=&quot;_ftnref4&quot; title=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;_ftnref4&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[4]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tứ tướng&lt;a href=&quot;#_ftn5&quot; name=&quot;_ftnref5&quot; title=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;_ftnref5&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;[5]&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ngộ chân không&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
